{"tid":1290691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［策略討論］如何對付忠義民團","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:05:26.000Z","uid":269052,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13a32e887a97373b7957421a6985205fc7434f14","tid":1290691,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:47:43.000Z","msg":"忠義民團既手法基本係十年如一日，佢地既套路係咁：<br />\n<br />\n一、用武力/指罵方式挑釁示威者<br />\n二、黑警例牌隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n三、示威者忍唔住手還手<br />\n四、忠義民團放大示威者既暴力，畀料藍絲Page<br />\n五、再進一步，就係拘捕示威者，放生忠義社團既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54p4SUe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54p4SUe.png&h=8e823f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20150906&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=54173937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20150906%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D54173937&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e0f14efb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20150906%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D54173937&h=523d5cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20150906&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=54173937</a> <br />\n【短片】警稱黃台仰「用手襲擊」警長倒地撞傷手重案跟進<br />\n<br />\n哩班人基本上係唔怕畀人拘捕，一黎佢地有免死金牌，二黎必要時佢地預左交個人出黎督下數<br />\n<br />\n佢個主腦阿Man係前黑警，更加係身披黃褂<br />\n<br />\n佢地好多時係對付和理非，將和理非變勇武<br />\n<br />\n利申，我唔係話要反對勇武，不過勇武一黎會中圈套，二黎又會犧牲幾個手足。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n民意事小，手足事大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日七七佢地又會出場，策略上，聽日係要對外宣傳，輸出革命，一亂就defeat左哩個計劃 （當然我知有巴絲唔認同哩個purpose)<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，對付忠義社團哩班勇武支共派，有乜計仔？"},{"pid":"c58c8d07d297c1377fe1fa18d2351a3665c2137a","tid":1290691,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"07316de6e2fa75f9529298a15b888936ce5d0fae","tid":1290691,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0b3c83837352fed865167b35fc635aabbfa80a54","tid":1290691,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"叫鳩達同佢再上擂台"}]}